This zip file contains the following files:

cclxpop.exe		The program
cclxpop.cfg		Sample configuration file
cclxpop.doc		Documentation
email1.bat		Sample batch file for use with LXMTA
email2.bat		sample batch file for use with LXPOP/LXNNTP



To use ccLXPOP, you must be able to connect to you ISP using LXPOP or LXMTA. These programs, and their documentation, are available at http:\\lxtcp.hplx.net

I recommend you read the documentation! Good Luck! 


